<p><b>M:</b> Supports RSA-MD5, as specified in
[RFC3961] page 31.</p>
</dd>
<dd>
<p><b>R:</b> Supports RC4-HMAC-MD5, as specified in <span><a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=90488" data-linktype="external">[RFC4757]</a></span>.</p>
